text: Abu Reza Fazlul Haque Bablu Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician. He was elected a member of parliament from Mymensingh-5 in February 1996. == Career == Bablu is a lawyer and president of Muktagachha Upazila BNP. He was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-5 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 15 February 1996 Bangladeshi general election. == References == Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi politicians Category:People from Mymensingh Division Category:6th Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Abu Reza Fazlul Haque Bablu
